{"title_page": "Eton blue", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2019}}\n{{Infobox color\n|title=Eton blue\n|hex=96C8A2\n|r=150|g=200|b=162\n|h=134|s=25 |v=78\n|source=[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eton_College]\n|spelling=Colour\n|isccname=Light yellowish green}}\n'''Eton blue''', or 'Shelduck Blue' is a greenish-blue colour used since early 19th century by sportsmen of [[Eton College]].<ref>http://www.etoncollege.com/EtonBlue.aspx</ref>{{deadlink|date=December 2019}} It is also used by [[Geelong Grammar School]] and is similar to the colour used by the [[University of Cambridge]] ([[Cambridge Blue (colour)|Cambridge Blue]]).\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of colours]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Shades of blue|Eton blue}}\n{{Shades of green}}\n\n[[Category:Shades of blue]]\n[[Category:Shades of green]]\n[[Category:Eton College]]\n[[Category:School colors]]\n\n\n{{Colour-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2019}}\n{{Infobox color\n|title=Eton blue\n|hex=96C8A2\n|r=150|g=200|b=162\n|h=134|s=25 |v=78\n|source=[http://www.etoncollege.com/EtonBlue.aspx Eton College]{{deadlink|date=December 2019}}\n|spelling=Colour\n|isccname=Light yellowish green}}\n'''Eton blue''', or 'Shelduck Blue' is a greenish-blue colour used since early 19th century by sportsmen of [[Eton College]].<ref>http://www.etoncollege.com/EtonBlue.aspx</ref>{{deadlink|date=December 2019}} It is also used by [[Geelong Grammar School]] and is similar to the colour used by the [[University of Cambridge]] ([[Cambridge Blue (colour)|Cambridge Blue]]).\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of colours]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Shades of blue|Eton blue}}\n{{Shades of green}}\n\n[[Category:Shades of blue]]\n[[Category:Shades of green]]\n[[Category:Eton College]]\n[[Category:School colors]]\n\n\n{{Colour-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Raquelbea", "label": "safe", "comment": "Fixed dead link", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eton_blue"}
